quran[55]{c,v,t}:
  54,1,IYure sele ifikile yaye nenyanga sele icandeke (kubini)
  54,2,"Ke kaloku xa bebona umqondiso (ummangaliso), bayatshikila bathi: “(Lo) ngumlingo ogqithayo.”"
  54,3,"Kananjalo baye baphika, balandela iminqweno yabo. Kodwa into nganye inexesha lokufezekiswa (kwayo)"
  54,4,Ke kaloku sele ifikile kubo inkcazelo ekukho kuyo isilumkiso (esaneleyo ngokubhekiselele kugabadelo)
  54,5,Ubulumko obuphangaleleyo kodwa isilumkiso asibancedi (nto)
  54,6,"Bayeke ke (Muhammad), ngeMini uMkhwazi aya kubizela abantu kwinto engathandekiyo (uMlilo wesiHogo)"
  54,7,"Amehlo abo aya kuba ethobekile, baya kuphuma emangcwabeni wabo bengathi ziinkumbi bethe saa"
  54,8,"Begxalathelana besiya phambili kuMkhwazi. Abangakholwayo baya kuthi: “Le yiMini enzima.”"
  54,9,"Abantu bakaNûh baphika ngaphambili kunabo, ke kaloku basiphika isiCaka seThu. Bathi: “ (Lo uNûh) yindoda ephambanayo” wada (uNûh) wagxothwa (ngabo)"
  54,10,"Ke kaloko wacela eNkosini yakhe: “Inene mna ndoyisakele, ndincede ke Wena (Nkosi yam).”"
  54,11,Thina ke Savula iingcango zezulu nemvula eyathululeka phantsi
  54,12,"Eyenza umhlaba wagqabhuka yimithombo namanzi, aza namanzi adibana nento eyayisele imiselwe kakade"
  54,13,Samthumela ke yena (ngenqanawa eyenziwe) ngamaplanga nezikhonkwane
  54,14,Idada phantsi kolondolozo lweThu njengomvuzo kulowo wayephikiwe (uNûh)
  54,15,"Sayishiya\tukuba\tibe\tngumqondiso1,\tukhona\tke\toza kukhumbula (okanye afumane isilumkiso)"
  54,16,Saba njani ke ukuba (buhlungu) isohlwayo saM nesilumkiso
  54,17,"Kananjalo Siyenze i’Kur’ân yalula ukuba ikhumbuleke, ukhona phofu oza kukhumbula"
  54,18,Ama’Ad aphika; saba njani ke (ukuba buhlungu) isohlwayo saM nesilumkiso
  54,19,"Inene, Thina Sathumela kubo umoya otswinayo ngemini eyayiyeyeshwangusha (elalisihla emva kweshwangusha)"
  54,20,Lincothula abantu ngokungathi zizibhukubhuku zemithi yesundu encothulwe neengcambu
  54,21,Saba njani (ukuba buhlungu) isohlwayo saM nesilumkiso
  54,22,"Kananjalo Siyenze yalula i’Kur’ân ukuba ikhumbuleke, ukhona phofu oza kukhumbula"
  54,23,AmaThamûd asala isilumkiso
  54,24,"Athi:“Ingabangumntuomnyephakathikwethuesizakulandela yena? Inene singaba sekulahlekeni nasempambanweni"
  54,25,Ingaba umyalezo uthunyelwe kuye phakathi kwethu? Hayi khona lixoki elingenazintloni (lo)!”
  54,26,"Baza\tkumazi\tngomso\tukuba\tngubani\tna\tolixoki elingenazintloni"
  54,27,"Inene Thina Sithumele ithokazi lenkamela ukuba libe luvavanyo kubo, bajonge ke ube nomonde"
  54,28,"Ubaxelele kananjalo okokuba amanzi baza kwahlulelana ngawo, (Nenkamela), ngenye (imini) kuza kusela bona (ize ibe yinkamela ngenye imini)"
  54,29,"Kodwa bona babiza ugxa wabo2, waba nesibindi wayinqumla imisipha"
  54,30,Saba njani ke (ukuba buhlungu) iSohlwayo saM nesilumkiso
  54,31,Inene Thina Sathoba isiqhushumbisi phezu kwabo baba ngathi ziintsasa ezomileyo ezizizijungqu zesibaya sezilwanyana
  54,32,"Kananjalo Siyenze i’Kur’ân yalula ukuba ikhumbuleke, ukhona na phofu oza kukhumbula"
  54,33,Abantu bakwaLût basala isilumkiso
  54,34,"Inene, Thina Sathumela isiphango samatye phezu kwabo ngaphandle kosapho lukaLût, lona Salusindisa phambi koms’obomvu"
  54,35,NgoBabalo oluvela kuThi. Simvuza kanjalo ke onombulelo
  54,36,"Ke kaloku yena wayesele ebalumkisile (kwantlandlolo) ngohlaselo lweThu, kodwa bona basiphikisa isilumkiso"
  54,37,"Kananjalo bafuna ukuxhwila iindwendwe zakhe, Kodwa Sabamfamekisela amehlo abo (SiSithi): “Ngcamlani isohlwayo saM nesilumkiso ke.”"
  54,38,Ke kaloku ekuseni bafikelwa sisohlwayo esibuhlungu
  54,39,"(Kwathiwa kubo): “Ngcamlani isohlwayo saM nesilumkiso ke.”"
  54,40,Kananjalo Siyenze i’Kur’ân yalula ukuba ikhumbuleke kodwa ukhona na phofu oza kukhumbula
  54,41,Kanti nakubantu bakwaFir’awn kwafika isilumkiso
  54,42,"Bayala imiqondiso yeThu yonke, Sabahlasela ke ngohlaselo lwaloWo Unobunganga, Unamandla"
  54,43,"Ingaba (abantu) abangakholwayo benu bangcono kunabayaa bamandulo, okanye ninogonyo oluvela kwiziBhalo"
  54,44,"Okanye bathi: “Thina silibandla elixhasanayo,” kusini na"
  54,45,"(Elo) bandlana labo liza koyiswa, kwaye baza kuza ngemiva (babaleke)"
  54,46,"Kodwa iYure lixesha labo elimisiweyo, kwaye iYure leyo ingaphaya ngokonakalisa yaye ikrakra ngakumbi"
  54,47,Inene izaphula-mthetho zisekulahlekeni nasempambanweni
  54,48,"NgeMini abaya kurhuqelwa eMlilweni ngobuso babo kuya (kuthiwa kubo): “Ngcamlani ukuchukunyiswa sisiHogo kaloku”"
  54,49,Inene Sidale zonke izinto ngommiselo (wento eziya kuba yiyo)
  54,50,"Ukanti\tumyalelo\tweThu\tuba\tmnye\tjwi\tube\tngathi kukuqhwanyaza kweliso"
  54,51,"Kananjalo Sele Sabatshabalalisa abanjengani, ukhona phofu za kukhumbula"
  54,52,Kananjalo yonke into abayenzayo ibhaliwe emacwecweni
  54,53,Kwaye nto nganye encinane (nenkulu) ibhaliwe
  54,54,Inene amalungisa aya kuba phakathi kwemiyezo nemilambo
  54,55,"Esihlalweni sentlonipheko ecaleni kukaSobunganga, uSomandla"